03:46.777 --> 03:49.712
You know, I like it better when you
come in with a good-lookin' detective

03:49.723 --> 03:51.883
- who buys cake.
- Right? Me too.

03:51.893 --> 03:53.885
You should call him.

03:53.895 --> 03:56.688
<i>No.</i> Again, he's just working me.

03:56.698 --> 04:00.458
So? Everybody's working
everybody until they're not.

04:00.468 --> 04:01.893
No, I saw something, Plum...

04:01.903 --> 04:03.561
The way Dominic was lookin' at you.

04:03.571 --> 04:05.029
It was clear, Plum, that man is...

04:05.039 --> 04:07.865
Whatever! He's not even my type.

04:07.875 --> 04:10.902
Dude, you've dated
only one person. Singular.

04:10.912 --> 04:13.104
You have no idea what your type is.

04:13.114 --> 04:15.573
<i>Dude,</i> this is a pointless conversation.

04:15.583 --> 04:18.543
- Even if I did like him...
- You do. I can tell.

04:18.553 --> 04:20.978
Even if I did...

04:20.988 --> 04:23.448
he's just... he just wants me
to talk about the case.

04:23.458 --> 04:25.283
That's called an opening.

04:25.293 --> 04:27.051
Do I have to do
all the work around here?

04:30.498 --> 04:33.992
Return of the Glamazons.

04:34.002 --> 04:35.960
It's awful for business,

04:35.970 --> 04:38.997
but I gotta say, this year,
I'm kinda into Fashion Week.

04:39.007 --> 04:44.002
If you are suddenly straight,
I'm gonna die of confusion.

04:44.012 --> 04:46.170
You're safe.

04:46.180 --> 04:47.839
No, I'm happy for <i> you.</i>

04:47.849 --> 04:50.341
You're doing that article
on the runway show.

04:50.351 --> 04:52.410
This is a good thing.
So when is it again?

04:52.420 --> 04:54.512
And... what are you gonna wear?

04:54.522 --> 04:58.283
I'm not. I am watching it online.

04:58.293 --> 05:00.918
Kitty's assistant gave me a link.

05:00.928 --> 05:03.354
Oh, you're watching it now? Lemme see.

05:03.364 --> 05:05.156
What do we got here?

05:05.166 --> 05:08.359
- What is this?
- I quit Y.

05:08.369 --> 05:13.031
It's phase one
of Verena's New Baptist Plan.

05:13.041 --> 05:15.967
"Side effects include
headaches, nausea, fatigue"...

05:15.977 --> 05:18.169
Well, that's Sunday
morning at my house...

05:18.179 --> 05:20.104
"heart palpitations, brain zaps"...

05:20.114 --> 05:23.141
- What the hell is a brain zap?
- Beats me.

05:23.151 --> 05:27.658
"Obsessive thoughts, paranoia,
hallucinations. Suicidal ideations"?

05:27.669 --> 05:28.670
Ok.

05:28.681 --> 05:30.982
No, no, no, you need
to stay on your meds.

05:30.992 --> 05:32.632
Forget Verena.

05:32.643 --> 05:34.952
You can go through insurance
and get your stomach stapled.

05:34.962 --> 05:38.856
Actually, I can't. I have to pay
out-of-pocket and get reimbursed.

05:38.866 --> 05:42.026
And I need more surgery after
the fact for my excess skin,

05:42.036 --> 05:44.262
which is considered cosmetic,
so they won't pay.

05:44.273 --> 05:45.563
Definitely can't afford that.

05:45.573 --> 05:47.665
I don't know about this, Plum.

05:47.675 --> 05:49.334
Have you vetted this woman?

05:49.344 --> 05:51.077
Yeah. Totally.

05:52.413 --> 05:54.172
I Googled her.

05:54.182 --> 05:57.041
She's given boatloads of money
to all kinds of lefty causes.

05:57.051 --> 05:58.910
OK, fine. Whatever.

05:58.920 --> 06:01.045
At least let me stay with you
till you get off the Y.

06:01.055 --> 06:02.847
It looks like it could be scary.

06:02.857 --> 06:05.416
Come on. I'm the girl
who never gets sick, remember?

06:05.426 --> 06:07.251
This isn't germ warfare.
These are chemicals

06:07.261 --> 06:09.520
that were helping your brain
and now are not.

06:09.530 --> 06:12.090
This is serious, Plum,
you can't take this lightly.

06:12.100 --> 06:15.426
Stop! I'm gonna hole up,
I'll relax, write my piece.

06:15.436 --> 06:18.596
It'll be like a withdrawal-cation...

06:18.606 --> 06:20.398
with some work on the side.

06:20.408 --> 06:23.534
Mm-hm. So you're not just
gonna lay up on the couch

06:23.544 --> 06:25.737
and binge-watch
those stupid nature shows?

06:25.747 --> 06:28.339
No. Working.

06:28.349 --> 06:30.583
The whole time. One hundred percent.

06:38.960 --> 06:40.784
Anyway, I'm going off the grid
for a few days.

06:40.795 --> 06:42.186
I just want to let you know.

06:42.196 --> 06:43.855
To write. I'll call you when I'm done.

06:43.865 --> 06:45.731
All right. Love you, Ma.

07:06.487 --> 07:07.645
<i> Hello.</i>

07:07.655 --> 07:09.080
Oh, hey. Hi.

07:09.090 --> 07:10.548
<i>This is Plum.</i>

07:10.558 --> 07:12.650
<i>Sorry to call instead of text.</i>

07:12.660 --> 07:14.452
No, I'm glad you did. What's up?

07:14.462 --> 07:15.987
Are you... busy?

07:15.997 --> 07:17.655
<i>No, no. Today's my day off.</i>

07:17.665 --> 07:20.224
It's nice to hear your voice.

07:20.234 --> 07:25.963
Um, I just wanted to let you
know that......

07:25.973 --> 07:28.900
- Is everything OK?
- <i>Yeah.</i>

07:28.910 --> 07:31.736
I was gonna call your phone
message and just say,

07:31.746 --> 07:33.271
"Hello, Detective,"

07:33.281 --> 07:35.226
I'm going out of town for a few days

07:35.237 --> 07:36.840
"in case you need
your beauty informant."

07:36.851 --> 07:38.943
And then just, like, hang up.

07:39.476 --> 07:40.875
My what?

07:42.132 --> 07:43.824
Beauty informant.

07:43.858 --> 07:47.418
Like a criminal informant,
but... beautiful.

07:47.428 --> 07:50.588
Oh. Yeah, yeah. Got it.

07:50.598 --> 07:52.523
<i>Hey, while I got you,</i>

07:52.533 --> 07:55.259
<i>do you know someone named Leeta?</i>

07:55.269 --> 07:58.629
You mean that, uh, weird girl
who works in the beauty closet?

07:58.639 --> 07:59.972
Yeah. You know her?

08:01.809 --> 08:03.943
Not really.

08:06.547 --> 08:08.840
Ahh, it's all right.
Don't worry about it.

08:12.520 --> 08:16.147
S... Yeah, so, you know, listen,
have a nice trip, and, uh,

08:16.157 --> 08:18.716
<i>don't be a hero, OK? When
it comes to helping me out.</i>

08:18.733 --> 08:21.514
We still don't know if these hackers
are connected to this homicide.

08:22.830 --> 08:25.623
- W-What homicide?
- <i>All I can say,</i>

08:25.633 --> 08:28.133
somebody in the Austen
Media family was murdered.

08:30.071 --> 08:32.697
Missing fashion photographer
Malleck Ferguson

08:32.707 --> 08:34.065
was found dead today.

08:34.075 --> 08:35.832
A surreal twist?

08:35.842 --> 08:38.836
Witnesses say his body
fell out of the sky.

08:38.846 --> 08:41.339
<i>So far, authorities have no leads,</i>

08:41.349 --> 08:44.041
but the FAA confirms that several planes

08:44.051 --> 08:46.477
were in the area before Ferguson's body

08:46.487 --> 08:48.913
hit a Lower East Side restaurant patio.

08:48.923 --> 08:51.415
More as this wild story develops.

08:51.425 --> 08:53.985
<i> All right, we're clear.</i>

08:53.995 --> 08:56.187
Send regrets to Jason Wu.

08:56.197 --> 08:58.689
I'm absolutely not going
to Yeezy this season.

08:58.699 --> 09:00.858
And find out what time
Victoria's show starts.

09:00.868 --> 09:03.594
I don't want to be sitting there
like some fool, waiting, again.

09:03.604 --> 09:05.897
- If I could go back in time...
- You can't. I just wish

09:05.907 --> 09:08.232
you were capable of learning
from your mistakes.

09:08.242 --> 09:10.768
Confirm my re-see with Rodarte,

09:10.778 --> 09:12.534
and then make sure
the helicopter is there

09:12.545 --> 09:14.211
to take me to the Open. I want...

09:15.349 --> 09:17.608
God! I know we joked about this, but...

09:17.618 --> 09:19.844
- The timing isn't a coincidence.
- Of course not.

09:19.854 --> 09:21.913
And dropping his body out of a plane?

09:21.923 --> 09:25.182
It's Fashion Week. They're already
calling this the Runway Murder.

09:25.192 --> 09:26.884
Focus. Please?

09:26.894 --> 09:29.353
This is bad. It could come back on us.

09:29.363 --> 09:32.023
We stood behind Malleck during
the first few rape allegations

09:32.033 --> 09:33.591
<i>and</i> that media boycott.

09:33.601 --> 09:35.793
How he got that girl
to recant, I'll never...

09:35.803 --> 09:38.537
Green tea, loose leaf,
not in some awful paper cup.

09:41.943 --> 09:44.702
- Not on the record.
- Mm-hm.

09:44.712 --> 09:49.874
We still paid for Malleck's legal
defense and... and his PR team.

09:49.884 --> 09:53.044
I'm sure there's something in all
our leaked information about it.

09:53.054 --> 09:56.247
Well, why would Austen Media
pay for Malleck's legal team?

09:56.257 --> 09:58.716
Because Malleck is...

09:58.726 --> 10:01.085
Was part of the family.

10:01.095 --> 10:02.887
If you, I don't know,

10:02.897 --> 10:05.156
liked to diddle golden retrievers,

10:05.166 --> 10:06.424
we'd do the same thing for you.

10:06.434 --> 10:08.659
Well, fortunately for both of us,

10:08.669 --> 10:09.961
I broke it off with Rover.

10:09.971 --> 10:12.463
Funny.

10:12.473 --> 10:15.766
If you get any Intel on
who's behind this, tell me.

10:15.776 --> 10:17.802
If the monsters who killed Malleck

10:17.812 --> 10:20.137
are the same ones who hacked us,

10:20.155 --> 10:22.823
Stanley, and his family,
could be targets.

10:24.352 --> 10:26.452
I could be a target.

10:28.456 --> 10:30.122
Or me.

10:31.659 --> 10:33.517
Yes. Also that.

10:33.527 --> 10:35.127
Just get on it, will you?

10:37.590 --> 10:39.616
<i>When the body dropped,
I thought it was fake.</i>

10:39.634 --> 10:41.258
<i>Like a Fashion Week stunt?</i>

10:41.268 --> 10:43.194
<i>Or that SVU show was filming.</i>

10:43.204 --> 10:45.696
<i>They're always coming up
with crazy ways to kill people.</i>

10:45.706 --> 10:47.031
<i>That show's been on forever.</i>

10:54.949 --> 10:58.442
<i>♪</i>- <i> So,</i> one bad guy murdered,

10:58.452 --> 11:01.812
<i>one brain zap, and some
remote fashion show viewing...</i>

11:01.822 --> 11:05.349
<i>So far, my withdrawal-cation
didn't seem so bad.</i>

11:05.359 --> 11:09.820
<i>But as some drunken</i> tailgaters and I

11:09.830 --> 11:12.490
<i>were about to find out,
it was just getting started.</i>

11:44.492 --> 11:46.891
- Synced and corrected by Shazi89 -
- www.addic7ed.com -

11:49.618 --> 11:51.985
<i>The two victims shown
here, French soccer players,</i>

11:51.996 --> 11:53.753
<i>were recently reported missing
from Paris,</i>

11:53.763 --> 11:57.256
<i>and appear to be the latest
victims of the Runway Murders.</i>

11:57.267 --> 11:58.725
I can't watch.

11:58.736 --> 12:00.295
Put it back on, jackass.

12:00.305 --> 12:02.471
Don't talk to him like that, jackass.

12:04.442 --> 12:06.558
<i>... unconfirmed reports of four more men</i>

12:06.569 --> 12:09.037
<i>dropped across New Jersey,
Rhode Island, and Pennsylvania,</i>

12:09.047 --> 12:11.906
<i>bringing the possible total
to seven victims.</i>

12:11.916 --> 12:14.208
- It's Jennifer! It has to be.
- Who's Jennifer?

12:14.218 --> 12:16.411
Stay current or you're fired, Ben.

12:16.421 --> 12:18.246
Not really.

12:18.256 --> 12:20.615
Oh, it just makes me sick.

12:20.625 --> 12:22.483
Hey, is Plum working today?

12:22.493 --> 12:24.552
Her singing, it calms me down, you know?

12:24.562 --> 12:26.754
It's like angels humming.

12:26.764 --> 12:28.122
She is not.

12:28.132 --> 12:31.292
Calm yourself by serving my customers.

12:31.302 --> 12:33.394
Absolutely, sir.

12:44.849 --> 12:46.841
Hey, there you are.

12:46.851 --> 12:49.077
- Hi.
- Well, you don't look suicidal to me.

12:49.087 --> 12:51.779
Thanks. I try. What's up?

12:51.789 --> 12:53.981
Listen, why don't you, um,

12:53.991 --> 12:55.483
why don't you stay on your meds

12:55.493 --> 12:56.784
and let Ben be your boyfriend?

12:56.794 --> 12:58.753
- Ugh.
- What? He's adorable.

12:58.763 --> 13:00.621
And your total disinterest in him

13:00.631 --> 13:02.156
got him beggin' like Rolo.

13:02.166 --> 13:03.791
No offense.

13:03.801 --> 13:05.860
He is adorable,
but I can't have sex thoughts

13:05.870 --> 13:08.363
about somebody who thinks
that Greenland is a continent.

13:08.373 --> 13:10.431
Yeah, that is pretty sad.

13:10.441 --> 13:12.133
He has no stomach for the news,

13:12.143 --> 13:14.335
much less my conspiracy theories.

13:14.345 --> 13:16.504
Speaking of which,
these Runway Murders...

13:16.514 --> 13:18.473
- La-la-la-la-la-la-la-la-la!
- What? What?

13:18.483 --> 13:21.109
No. Total media blackout.
I have to work.

13:21.119 --> 13:23.277
I want no negative vibes
while I withdraw.

13:23.287 --> 13:24.458
- Oh, come on...
- I promise,

13:24.469 --> 13:26.180
I will juice with you about everything

13:26.190 --> 13:29.200
- as soon as I'm back on the grid.
- OK, but the soup, right? It's lo-cal...

13:29.211 --> 13:31.052
- I'll talk to you soon.
- Plum...

13:31.062 --> 13:32.720
- Call me, all right?
- Thank you.

13:32.730 --> 13:34.188
<i>Call me!</i>

13:36.534 --> 13:39.727
<i> The withdrawals?
Yeah, they were no joke.</i>

13:39.737 --> 13:41.629
<i>I started</i> seeing <i> things.</i>

13:48.246 --> 13:50.738
<i>I started answering
Kitty's Girls emails...</i>

13:50.748 --> 13:52.840
<i>Inappropriately.</i>

13:52.850 --> 13:55.076
<i>"Before I can answer your question,"</i>

13:55.086 --> 13:57.145
<i>I'd like to ask if you get pleasure</i>

13:57.155 --> 13:59.480
<i>from inserting tampons into your vagina?</i>

13:59.490 --> 14:01.516
<i>Because I don't. But if you do,</i>

14:01.526 --> 14:03.684
<i>"then that's no one's damn business."</i>

14:05.563 --> 14:07.655
<i>At least I was safe in my apartment</i>

14:07.665 --> 14:09.891
<i>with my nature documentaries.</i>

14:09.901 --> 14:12.493
<i>Except there is no safe place</i>

14:12.503 --> 14:14.538
<i>when you're going through withdrawal.</i>

14:14.549 --> 14:16.097
<i>the smaller gazelle.</i>

14:16.107 --> 14:18.099
<i>He makes his approach.</i>

14:18.109 --> 14:20.668
<i>And now, the hunt is on.</i>

14:22.213 --> 14:23.771
<i>Ohh. I have a corn.</i>

14:23.781 --> 14:26.107
It really hurts.

14:26.117 --> 14:27.917
Do you see anything?

14:33.257 --> 14:36.517
You look like hell.

14:36.527 --> 14:38.427
I'm starving.

14:40.231 --> 14:41.797
I don't have any cereal.

14:44.602 --> 14:46.594
Cereal?

14:46.604 --> 14:48.296
I'm a damn animal.

14:48.306 --> 14:51.232
I eat meat, Plum.

14:51.242 --> 14:53.367
Where the hell's the real food?

14:53.377 --> 14:55.970
- That is my <i> real</i> food.
- No it's not.

14:55.980 --> 14:58.406
You ever been to Mauritania?

14:58.416 --> 15:00.608
Isn't that in West Africa?

15:00.618 --> 15:03.911
Men in Mauritania
love big women so much.

